OL,6,FA councillor faced an official
OL,7,Fcomplaint for refusing to sign a "get
OL,8,Fwell soon" card.
OL,10,FThe grievance was among 223 registered
OL,11,Fby North Yorkshire Council between
OL,12,FApril last year and June this year,
OL,13,Faccording to the Local Democracy
OL,14,FReporting Service.
OL,16,FThe list also included allegations
OL,17,Fthat a meeting was "shouty and
OL,18,Fsweary", along with poor email
OL,19,Fetiquette.
