OL,3,CCouncillor faced official complaint
OL,4,Cfor refusing to sign card
OL,6,FA report for North Yorkshire Council's
OL,7,Fstandards and governance committee
OL,8,Fsaid the volume of complaints meant
OL,9,Fofficials were struggling to cope.
OL,11,FA "high proportion" related to just
OL,12,Fthree parish councils but the council
OL,13,Fhas declined to reveal which ones.
OL,15,FOf the 179 complaints assessed so far,
OL,16,F145 merited no further action -
OL,17,Fincluding the complaint about the "get
OL,18,Fwell soon" card.
